data.description: VA Assumable @ 3.25% for $213,000  *New Roof 2022*  Inside HVAC 2017.   This split level features a large and privacy fenced corner lot with yard building and screened porch with additional lockout storage.  You'll appreciate the Recent Upgrades to include cabinets, granite, interior doors, lighting, flooring, tile work, refinished tubs, and an *Electric Fireplace* being installed Feb 19th.  First floor Primary Bedroom with Walk In closet and Tile Shower / Tub combo.  Family room is central to the home and provides easy kitchen access via a 'server's window' - perfect for Movie Night!  Laundry and Half Bath also on first floor.  Upstairs find (3) bedrooms which share a Full Bath with Tile Shower and Tub Combo.  *NO HOA - Plenty of room for BOAT or RV PARKING*.  Space to ADD A GARAGE.
